      "releaseNotes": "What’s new in 3.9:\n\nObservation Deck: Your Merlin home screen now features a swipeable daily feed showcasing Bird of the Day, stunning featured photos, and bite-sized bird tips! Each contains a full-screen view for photos and videos, plus a \"Learn more\" button to dive deeper into species accounts or related content.\n\nHabitat Photos: Discover where birds live with our new carousel of habitat photos curated for a subset of species, making it easier than ever to find the birds near you or further afield!\n\nNew language support for Kyrgyz and Welsh.\n\nImprovements and new species added to Photo ID.\n\nBug fixes and improvements.",
